description:
Padded gilet with quilted red lining. Red pocket zippers to match body zip. Completely stealth with no branding, only Neck label and custom tab on the bottom. Ideal for layering with a sweatshirt or hood on those cold nights.

name: Classic crest polo (stealth series)
description:
The classic crest applied to our premium fitted polo shirts. Crafted using soft thread for the logo and the signature in plush red velvet. Our premium polo shirts have the softest yarn and can be compared with t-shirts in comparison to the traditional polo shirt yarn. They also haven’t been embroidered direct to the garment but instead as a panel then applied, this way no feeling from the embroidery will be on the inside plus gives a much tighter stitch for the design.

100% Premium ringspun cotton – 170gsm 
Custom Tags on neckline and ribbing 
Black polo shirt with embroidered application, hand crafted in our factory in South London.

name: Royalty Tag (Glow Ink)
description:
A collaboration piece between Royalty Wear X Dark (Graffiti Artist).

The concept of the design is to have a simple tag inspired by street life graffiti but with the added effect of the dripping glow ink. The ink is "uv reactive" which means it will glow bright green after being exposed to light. In normal day to day wear it is an ivory white print.
 
100% Premium ringspun cotton – 165gsm 
Custom Tags on neckline and ribbing 
Black shirt with soft hand print, screen printed in our factory in South London.

name: Welcome to the Jungle
description:
A collaboration piece between Royalty Wear X Geo Designs.

One of our best graphic prints to date using the fierce tiger (with a whole load of teeth!), this design has been manipulated using the “kaleidoscope technique” with the simple and highlighted message of “Welcome to the Jungle”. This is print has virtually no print feel and is extremely soft.
 
100% Premium ringspun cotton – 165gsm
Custom Tags on neckline and ribbing 
Black shirt with soft hand print, screen printed in our factory in South London.

name: Ice Cream T-shirt
description:
A collaboration piece between Royalty Wear X Funny Tummy.

Touching back on the roots of "Art". Featuring the artistic skills of one of the UK’s most up and coming artists Funny Tummy, from his artwork being noticed by Rihanna and working with Adidas, Tinie Tempah, Wretch 32…you can’t get bigger than this. Playing on the concept of juicy lips licking an ice cream breaking up the design in lines makes you focus more on the details and appreciate the vibrant colours.

100% Premium ringspun cotton – 165gsm 
Custom Tags on neckline and ribbing 
Black shirt with soft hand print, screen printed in our factory in South London.
